#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:1
msgid "E4119"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `unknown_func_labelled_arg`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`unknown_func_labelled_arg`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:5
msgid ""
"This function is not a toplevel function, so it cannot have labelled "
"arguments."
msgstr "该函数不是顶层函数，因此不能带有标签参数。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:7
msgid ""
"Only toplevel functions can declare or receive labelled arguments. Local "
"functions are inferred as ordinary function values, so a call such as "
"`g(x~)` is rejected when `g` is a local function parameter."
msgstr "只有顶层函数才能声明或接收标签参数。局部函数会被推断为普通函数值，因此当 `g` 是局部函数参数时，`g(x~)` 这样的调用会被拒绝。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:13
msgid ""
"fn init {\n"
"  let x = 42\n"
"  fn f(g) {\n"
"    g(x~)\n"
"  //^\n"
"  // Error: This function is not a toplevel function, so it cannot have "
"labelled arguments.\n"
"  }\n"
"  f(h)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn h(x : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(x)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:19
msgid ""
"Pass the value positionally when calling a local function value, or move "
"the function to the toplevel if you need labelled arguments."
msgstr "调用局部函数值时，请按位置传递参数；如果需要标签参数，请将函数移动到顶层。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4119.md:22
msgid ""
"fn init {\n"
"  let x = 42\n"
"  fn f(g) {\n"
"    g(x)\n"
"  }\n"
"  f(h)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn h(x : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(x)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#~ msgid "Erroneous example"
#~ msgstr "错误示例"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "fn main {\n"
#~ "  fn greet(name~ : String) -> Unit {\n"
#~ "    println(\"Hello, \\{name}\")\n"
#~ "  }\n"
#~ "}"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid "Suggestion"
#~ msgstr "建议"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can either remove the labelled "
#~ "argument, using positional argument instead:"
#~ msgstr "您可以删除带标签的参数，改用位置参数代替："

#~ msgid ""
#~ "fn main {\n"
#~ "  fn greet(name : String) -> Unit {\n"
#~ "    println(\"Hello, \\{name}\")\n"
#~ "  }\n"
#~ "  greet(\"world\")\n"
#~ "}"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid "Or you can make the function a toplevel function:"
#~ msgstr "或者您可以将函数设为顶层函数："

#~ msgid ""
#~ "fn greet(name~ : String) -> Unit {\n"
#~ "  println(\"Hello, \\{name}\")\n"
#~ "}\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "fn main {\n"
#~ "  greet(name=\"World\")\n"
#~ "}"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Current MoonBit reports this pattern as"
#~ " [E4114](./E4114.md). See E4114 for the "
#~ "checked examples and fixes."
#~ msgstr "当前 MoonBit 会将这种模式报告为 [E4114](./E4114.md)。请参阅 E4114 中已检查的示例和修复方式。"
